reviews.review_text: Cameron Stadium Thanks very much for uploading these FOBs.  4 friends and I drove down from DC for the show 3 nights later at William&Mary, Williamsburg.  We had great fun, with another Bertha>GoodLovin'; but in hindsight Duke was the place to be.  I appreciate the work and dedication of the early audience tapers - it must've been a madhouse :-)  Are you the original taper?  I ask because in the youtube video of GoodLovin' we see a mic stand above the crowd, in the final 30 sec or so of the tune.
re: Cameron Yes, those are my mics on the youtube Good Lovin'! Thanks for pointing it out.
